query:
UPDATE runtime_sessions
            SET rts_status = $1::running_status,
                initial_data = $2,
                latest_step_idx = $3,
                latest_result = $4,
                updated_at = $5,
                step_execution_times = $6,
                step_ids = $7,
                total_execution_time = $8
            WHERE global_uuid = $9
